This is Valve's de_aztec with some miner changes. no rain. no barrells. Different textures here and there. Better frame per second. First 2 screenshots show the hall that is added from T spawn to B bombsite. evens the game play.
This map was liked so much on our server it replaced De_aztec. Your not gonna regret this download.
You can also get this and other maps at our website snpub.com.
